metadata_nft.name: Eye of Eleriah #213
metadata_nft.description: This NFT is a window into Project Eluüne's metaverse, it will transform into facets of our story-universe until you decide to lock it. Once locked it won't transform again. The choice is yours to make: Lock for what you see and lose what potentially comes next. Or give up the current artwork to never have it come out again and wait for the next cycle… A locked Eye will say "Locked Forever" in its attributes.
